# 🧹 Smart Duplicate File Cleaner

A Python-based automation tool to detect and remove duplicate files efficiently using checksum (MD5 hashing) with database logging support using MySQL.

---

## 📌 Features

- 🔍 Detects duplicate files using MD5 checksum
- 🗑️ Safe deletion using Send2Trash (Recycle Bin)
- 🖥️ Simple GUI built with Tkinter
- 🗄️ MySQL database integration for logging
- 📊 Tracks scanned files and deleted records
- ⚡ Progress tracking using TQDM

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Tkinter (GUI)
- MySQL
- hashlib (MD5)
- Send2Trash
- TQDM

---

## 📂 Project Structure
Duplicate_file_cleaner_project/
│
├── gui.py # GUI interface
├── scanner.py # File scanning & checksum logic
├── deleter.py # Duplicate deletion logic
├── db.py # Database connection
├── config.py # DB configuration
├── test_db.py # DB test file
├── requirements.txt # Required libraries
└── README.md


